org.moeaframework.util.tree

Class Not

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.moeaframework.util.tree.Node
      • org.moeaframework.util.tree.Not

  • public class Not
extends Node
    The node for calculating the logical NOT of a boolean value. The inputs and outputs to this node are shown below:
    Name Type Description
    Argument 1 Boolean The boolean value
    Return Value Number The logical NOT of the boolean value
